EXPECTED OUTPUT: error toast should display "Login failed"


// Test the ordering page
INPUT: Select no items
EXPECTED OUTPUT: Error toast should display "No Items Selected"
INPUT: Select one ore more items
EXPECTED OUTPUT: Total should update to be the sum of prices of the selected items
INPUT: Press "Order"
EXPECTED OUTPUT: Toast "Order Submitted" should appear 
EXPECTED OUTPUT: Order Object with unique id should appear in database 


